<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong><span>大湾区首场|</span></strong><strong><span>麻省理工学院</span></strong></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong><span>“飞向太空”主题开放日</span></strong></span></p>
